{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202", "id": 21916877, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUyMTkxNjg3Nw==", "number": 10202, "title": "std::rand::reseeding: infinite recursion in fill_bytes()", "user": {"login": "telotortium", "id": 1755789, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE3NTU3ODk=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1755789?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium", "html_url": "https://github.com/telotortium", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/telotortium/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2013-10-31T18:39:20Z", "updated_at": "2013-11-01T13:26:24Z", "closed_at": "2013-11-01T13:26:24Z", "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "The example code for `std::rand::Rng::fill_bytes` fails due to a stack overflow:\n\n``` rust\nuse std::rand::{task_rng, Rng};\n\nfn main() {\n   let mut v = [0u8, .. 13579];\n   task_rng().fill_bytes(v);\n   println!(\"{:?}\", v);\n}\n```\n\nThis is due to infinite recursion in the `ReseedingRng` trait (src/libstd/rand/reseeding.rs:72):\n\n``` rust\n    fn fill_bytes(&mut self, dest: &mut [u8]) {\n        self.reseed_if_necessary();\n        self.bytes_generated += dest.len();\n        self.fill_bytes(dest)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n`self.fill_bytes(dest)` should be `self.rng.fill_bytes(dest)` -- changing the line to that fixes the issue.\n", "closed_by": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/10202/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": "completed"}